{"tid":522584,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中國傳周四起全面禁止翻牆　企業須事先註冊","createTime":"2018-01-07T16:53:02.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-27T06:46:29.000Z","uid":39464,"like":140,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":68,"replies":[{"pid":"66d699262821292851a7d0f94ba4fbe225f769bd","tid":522584,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-07T16:53:02.000Z","msg":"內地對網絡一向有嚴格控制，據海外傳媒報道，內地最大國營電訊公司中國電信近日發布通知，敲定將於周四（11日）全面封鎖VPN及SD-WAN（即「翻牆」）接入，屆時企業用戶有意繼續使用VPN或SD-WAN，必須要事先向所屬商用網絡服務供應商註冊及申請。<br />\n<br />\n報道又指，事實上中國電信早在2017年7月已發出通知，上述措施將會在2018年2月前實施，包括禁止讓個人使用VPN，企業日後亦只能用以連接其海外總部的網站，禁止用以連結其他海外網站，而今次是首次有具體的實施日期。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20180107/bkncn-20180107185212007-0107_05011_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fcn%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180107%2Fbkncn-20180107185212007-0107_05011_001.html&d=C5URjvjJw%2FhmANx1N%2Fa7TwhMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=4f660713\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20180107/bkncn-20180107185212007-0107_05011_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"9144e3b7103046eaa29e1f2316b9a8529f02af52","tid":522584,"uid":26752,"like":90,"dislike":0,"score":90,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-07T16:59:38.000Z","msg":"係就快啦<br />\n死支蛆又要翻牆又要死去YouTube <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ff1ba404a53936e64221f451326c2d46cbbc378","tid":522584,"uid":39167,"like":11,"dislike":47,"score":-36,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-01-07T17:01:15.000Z","msg":"封埋香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8cc14c2cb8ff5859beb21b28a3deb18984ee14e","tid":522584,"uid":13303,"like":83,"dislike":0,"score":83,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-07T17:01:51.000Z","msg":"屌block到未呀講左九年都係咁多支那人"},{"pid":"59e9435c4303ab0590ee520cf7948ce243a93b62","tid":522584,"uid":77717,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"b8cc14c2cb8ff5859beb21b28a3deb18984ee14e","tid":522584,"uid":13303,"like":83,"dislike":0,"score":83,"citedBy":2,"replyTi